      <title>[오늘의 날씨] 2025년 3월 6일</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/03/06/EKNUCOWS3JEFZMDKMK7KMPCVIE/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/03/06/EKNUCOWS3JEFZMDKMK7KMPCVIE/</guid>
